  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Westerlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Presumed location of Lann&#39;s Point\"><img alt=\"Presumed location of Lann&#39;s Point\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/300px-The_Westerlands.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/450px-The_Westerlands.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/600px-The_Westerlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 57.8%; left: 6.9%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"Presumed location of Lann&#39;s Point\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Lann&#39;s Point\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Lann's Point</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Presumed location of Lann's Point\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Lann's Point</b> is a location in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lann%27s_Point&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_IV_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel IV Lannister\">Lancel IV Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">King of the Rock</a>, slew <a href=\"/index.php/Harrald_Halfdrowned\" title=\"Harrald Halfdrowned\">Harrald Halfdrowned</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> king, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Lann%27s_Point\" title=\"Battle of Lann&#39;s Point\">Battle of Lann's Point</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lann%27s_Point&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Presumably Lann's Point is found in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> and named after <a href=\"/index.php/Lann_the_Clever\" title=\"Lann the Clever\">Lann the Clever</a>. It potentially refer to the big peninsula west of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lann%27s_Point&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span